                  Special Thanksgiving Fare Sale
      Hurry! Purchase Tickets by Wednesday, November 21, 2001
      -------------------------------------------------------

US Airways is offering big discounts for travel during the Thanksgiving holiday period with fares as low as $98 roundtrip. These sale fares are available between most cities in the U.S. and between the U.S. and Canada or to many of our European destinations.  To take advantage of this offer, just book online at http://www.usairways.com/promotions/specials/thanksgiving_sale.htm no later than November 21, 2001. 

- Travel may originate on November 22 or 23, 2001 
- Return travel applies November 22, 23, 27, 28 or 29, 2001 
- All travel must be completed by November 29, 2001 
- Travel is not permitted November 24, 25 or 26, 2001 	 
- See Sale Fare Requirements below for complete details.

Plus, earn double Dividend Miles on flights between now and December 15, 2001. Be sure to register for this offer before departure at http://www.usairways.com/dividendmiles/7437.htm or call 1-800-872-4738 and enter Bonus Request Number 7437.

This is just a sample of the sale fares offered.  For reservations and fares from your city go to http://www.usairways.com/promotions/specials/thanksgiving_sale.htm


